<p>These messages prioritize family-like closeness, making them suitable for very close friendships. Remember to personalize them to reflect your specific situation and relationship.</p>
<p>I'm truly sorry for hurting you.  My actions were wrong, and I deeply regret causing you pain.  I value our relationship more than words can say.</p>
<li>I am so incredibly sorry.</li>
<li>Please forgive me; I messed up badly.</li>
<li>My deepest apologies for my hurtful actions.</li>
<li>I'm truly ashamed of myself.</li>
<li>I regret my words/actions deeply.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry; it was never my intention to hurt you.</li>
<li>I'm heartbroken that I caused you pain.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincerest apologies.</li>
<li>Forgive me, I feel terrible about what happened.</li>
<li>I'm sorry from the bottom of my heart.</li>
<li>I was wrong, and I take full responsibility.</li>
<li>Please know I value our relationship immensely.</li>
<li>I'm working on being better.</li>
<li>I deeply regret hurting you; it pains me greatly.</li>
<li>I hope you can find it in your heart to forgive me.</li>
    

